metadata.name: Elderly Elephant (pre reveal)
metadata.description: (Not revealed yet) Elderly Elephants is a community-driven NFT project with the core mission of supporting the building of schools in underserved areas of West Africa. Our Founders believe that Access to Education is a fundamental Human Right akin to Access to Healthcare, Clean Drinking Water, & the Internet. As such, we are 100% committed to providing transformative change to our targeted communities in need.
